# Capture-on-failure forensic bundles (design §B) — pcaps, per-container logs, conntrack/firewall state,
# rendezvous mailbox, resolved-env snapshots. Written by run-interop.sh under diag/<family>/<scenario>/ on
# a failure; a local footprint only (CI uploads it as an artifact). Never checked in.
diag/

# Local tee'd harness logs.
*.log
